description: Moscow has set it sights on gaining control of the Donbas, Ukraine's industrial heartland. title: IAS couple dog walking row: Mahua, Omar question transfers to Arunachal, Ladakh | Internet in splits
description: A massive controversy has erupted in the national capital after a picture of an IAS couple walking their dog in Thyagraj Stadium went viral. Sanjeev Khirwar and Rinku Dugga, both 1994 batch officers of the AGMUT cadre, were forcing athletes to finish their training by 7 PM, so that they could bring their dog to the facility for daily evening walk. The Ministry of Home Affairs has now transferred the couple to Arunachal Pradesh and Ladakh. However, TMC MP Mahua Moitra and NC Leader Omar Abdullah have slammed this punishment posting claiming that it was demoralising to the people there to be given the impression that officers only get sent as a punishment. Meanwhile, the internet is in splits as the 2 officers have been sent to opposite ends of the country. Memes went viral asking who will take care of the dog amid all of this. Watch this video for more details.|#IASCouple #Dog #ThyagrajStadium #SanjeevKhirwar #RinkuDugga #ArunachalPradesh #Ladakh #Delhi #MHA #Centre #DelhiGovernment #ModiGovernment

title: Imran Khan heaps praise on India amid fuel price hike in Pak; Lauds Modi govtтАЩs strategy
description: Former Pakistan PM Imran Khan has once again praised India. Hitting out at the Shehbaz Sharif government for hiking fuel prices in Pakistan, Imran lauded India for being able to reduce fuel prices amid cheaper oil from Russia. In a series of tweets, Imran said the highest price hike is the price Pakistan will pay for the incompetent and insensitive government. "In contrast India, strategic ally of the U.S., has managed to reduce fuel prices by Pkr 25 per litre by buying cheaper oil from Russia. Now our nation will suffer another massive dose of inflation at the hands of this cabal of crooks." tweeted Imran. The Shehbaz Sharif government in Pakistan increased the prices of all petroleum products by Pak rupees (PKR) 30/litre to reduce fuel subsidies. The highest-ever increase in the prices of all petroleum products in one go is aimed at impressing the International Monetary Fund. title: POKER UM DEN PAZIFIK: Chinas Machtanspruch in der S├╝dsee schreckt den Westen auf
description: Westliche Staaten haben alarmiert auf ein geplantes Kooperationsabkommen Chinas mit mehreren S├╝dpazifik-Staaten reagiert. Peking versuche, seinen Einfluss in der Region zu vergr├╢├Яern, sagte am Donnerstag der neue australische Premierminister Anthony Albanese. Auch die US-Regierung warnte die Pazifikstaaten vor "undurchsichtigen" Abkommen mit Peking. Der chinesische Au├Яenminister Wang Yi wies die Kritik zur├╝ck.|Chinas Entwurf des Pakts mit dem Titel "Gemeinsame Entwicklungsvision" sieht eine weitreichende Zusammenarbeit in den Bereichen Sicherheit und Wirtschaft vor. Geplant ist demnach eine millionenschwere Unterst├╝tzung Chinas f├╝r zehn Inselstaaten.┬а|Der Vertragsentwurf bietet ihnen auch die Aussicht auf ein Freihandelsabkommen mit Peking und Zugang zu Chinas riesigem Markt. Im Gegenzug w├╝rde die Volksrepublik an der Polizeiausbildung und dem Ausbau der Cybersicherheit beteiligt und erhielte besseren Zugang zu nat├╝rlichen Ressourcen vor Ort.|Die US-Regierung bef├╝rchtet nach Angaben des Au├Яenministeriums, dass die Abkommen "in einem ├╝bereilten, intransparenten Prozedere" ausgehandelt werden k├╢nnten. Bei China gebe es ein "Muster, undurchsichtige, vage Deals mit wenig Transparenz oder regionalen Absprachen" anzubieten, sagte Au├Яenamtssprecher Ned Price.|Auch Australiens Premierminister Albanese warnte vor dem wachsenden Einfluss Chinas in der Region. Australien m├╝sse darauf reagieren und sein Engagement im Pazifik-Raum verst├дrken, sagte er.|Die neuseel├дndische Premierministerin Jacinda Ardern erkl├дrte, die Region habe keinen Bedarf an Pekings Unterst├╝tzung im Sicherheitsbereich. "Wir sind der festen ├Ьberzeugung, dass wir im Pazifik-Raum ├╝ber die Mittel und die F├дhigkeit verf├╝gen, auf alle bestehenden Sicherheitsherausforderungen zu reagieren", sagte sie.|Der chinesische Au├Яenminister Wang Yi, der am Donnerstag eine mehrt├дgige Reise durch acht Pazifik-Staaten antrat, wies die Vorw├╝rfe zur├╝ck. "Chinas Zusammenarbeit mit den pazifischen Inselstaaten richtet sich nicht gegen ein bestimmtes Land", sagte er bei seinem Besuch in Honiara, der Hauptstadt der Salomonen.|Er warnte andere L├дnder vor Einmischung in der Angelegenheit. "Alle pazifischen Inselstaaten haben das Recht, ihre eigenen Entscheidungen zu treffen." Der Pakt k├╢nnte am Montag beschlossen werden, wenn Wang auf den Fidschi-Inseln mit den Au├Яenministern der Region zusammentrifft.|Der S├╝dpazifik wird zunehmend zum Schauplatz des Wettbewerbs zwischen China und den USA. Zuletzt unterzeichnete es mit den Salomonen bereits ein weitreichendes Sicherheitsabkommen.┬а|Die USA und Australien bef├╝rchten seit langem, dass China einen Milit├дrst├╝tzpunkt im S├╝dpazifik errichten k├╢nnte. title: Fakta-fakta Sungai Aare Swiss, Lokasi Hilangnya Emmeril Anak Sulung Ridwan Kamil
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Dikabarkan anak sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz (Eril), hilang terseret arus Sungai Aare, Bern, Swiss, Kamis (26/5/2022).||||Dalam keterangan resminya, adik Ridwan Kamil, Elpi Nazmuzaman menuturkan kejaidan berawal saat Eril berenang di Sungai Aare, Bern, bersama adik dan kawannya.||||Berikut sejumlah fakta mengenai Sungai Aare lokasi Emmeril terseret arus:||||Mengutip situs web Kota Bern, Jumat (27/5/2022), Sungai Aare bukan lokasi asing bagi warga lokal maupun turis.||||Baca Juga Kronologi Anak Ridwan Kamil Diduga Terseret Arus Saat Berenang di Sungai Aaree Swiss di https://www.kompas.tv/article/293083/kronologi-anak-ridwan-kamil-diduga-terseret-arus-saat-berenang-di-sungai-aaree-swiss||||Sungai Terpanjang di Swiss||||Dengan panjang 288 kilometer, Aare adalah sungai terpanjang yang mengalir sepenuhnya di Swiss bermuara di gletser Aar Bawah dan Atas di Bernese Oberland dan rutenya ke utara berakhir di Koblenz.||||Warisan Budaya Takbenda Swiss||||Sejak 2017, berenang di Sungai Aare merupakan tradisi dan karenanya masuk daftar warisan budaya tak benda UNESCO.||||Rekor Dunia Arung Jeram||||Rekor dunia untuk arung jeram Sungai Aare dibuat di Bern pada 2012, ketika total 1.268 orang secara bersamaan mengarungi sungai tersebut dengan perahu karet, dari Kiesen ke Eichholz.||||Lokasi Tradisi Zibeleschwmme||||Zibeleschwmme merupakan tradisi berenang di Sungai Aare saat musim dingin. Setelah berenang, mereka pun menghangatkan diri dengan suara karnaval "musik Guggen," teh panas, dan sup.||||Bagi Perenang Berpengalaman||||Berenang di Aare direkomendasikan hanya untuk perenang berpengalaman.||||Video Editor: Rengga||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/293087/fakta-fakta-sungai-aare-swiss-lokasi-hilangnya-emmeril-anak-sulung-ridwan-kamil

title: Kondisi Terkini Pencarian Anak Ridwan Kamil di Swiss
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV   - Saat mendapatkan informasi mengenai hilangnya Emmeril Khan Mumtadz atau Eril, sang ayah Ridwan Kamil yang sedang berada di Inggris segera menuntaskan kegiatannya dan langsung menuju Swiss.||||"Pada saat beliau berkegiatan beliau mendapatkan kabar dari keluarga mengenai hilang kontak Eril dan keluarga pada Kamis 26 Mei 2022. Setelah menerima kabar tersebut bapak Gubernur Jabar menuntaskan kegiatan di Inggris dan ke Swiss. Ridwan Kamil tiba di Bern, Swiss, Jumat (26/5/2022) pukul 1 waktu setempat."ujar Kepala Bagian Materi dan Komunikasi Pimpinan Biro Administrasi Pimpinan Pemprov Jabar Akhmad Taufiqurrachman.||||Baca Juga Anak Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Khan Mumtadz Hilang Teseret Arus Sungai di Swiss! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292998/anak-ridwan-kamil-emmeril-khan-mumtadz-hilang-teseret-arus-sungai-di-swiss||||Pihak kepolisian Swiss melanjutkan proses pencarian dengan jangkauan yang lebih luas mulai pukul 9 pagi waktu setempat.||||"Kepolisian Swiss melanjutkan jangkauan pencarian pada jumat 9 pagi Swiss. Kami atas nama Pemda Jabar sangat berharap dan ajak masyarakat agar kang Eril ditemukan sehat. Kami mengajak rekan-rekan media menjaga privasi bapak gubernur."ucap Akhmad Taufiqurrachman.||||Video Editor: Febi|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/293085/kondisi-terkini-pencarian-anak-ridwan-kamil-di-swiss

title: PM Modi inaugurates Bharat Drone Mahotsav at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi
description: Prime Minister Shri Narendra Modi will inaugurate India's biggest Drone Festival - Bharat Drone Mahotsav 2022 - on 27 May 2022 at 10 AM at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi.|Prime Minister will also interact with kisan drone pilots, witness open-air drone demonstrations and interact with startups in the drone exhibition centre.|Bharat Drone Mahotsav 2022 is a two day event and is being held on 27th and 28th May. Over 1600 delegates comprising government officials, foreign diplomats, armed forces, central armed police forces, PSUs, private companies and drone startups etc. will participate in the Mahotsav. More than 70 exhibitors will display various use cases of drones at the exhibition. Mahotsav will also witness a virtual award of drone pilot certificates, product launches, panel discussions, flying demonstrations, display of a Made in India Drone Taxi prototype, among others.|Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/8qsb5E Stay Updated! title: 'Deceit in garb of ceasefire': Indian Army tears into Pak for pushing terror in Kashmir
description: Indian Army has hit out at Pakistan after three infiltrators were gunned near LoC in J&K's Kupwara yesterday. The Indian Army said that exporting terrorism in J&K has been a state policy of Pakistan for last three decades. Three heavily-armed terrorists from Pakistan were intercepted and killed by the forces in Kupwara. There has been a surge in infiltration attempts from Pakistan since the last many weeks along the LoC in J&K. The surge in terror infiltrations comes at a time when a ceasefire is in place on the border between India and Pakistan. title: Pak buckles under IMF pressure as Sharif govt hikes petrol and diesel prices by Rs 30
description: Cash strapped Pakistan increased the price of petroleum products by Rs 30 per litre. After the increase, the price of one litre petrol will be at Rs 179.85 and diesel at Rs 174.15 in Pakistan. Similarly, the kerosene in Pakistan now costs  Rs 155.95 per litre and light diesel at Rs 148.41. Pakistan finance minister Miftah Ismail made the announcement at a press conference last evening. The decision was announced a day after the talks between the pakistan govt & IMF failed to reach an agreement on an economic bailout and the IMF staff-level agreement for the revival of the usd 6 billion programme ended. Watch the full video for more.|#Pakistan #ShehbazSharif #Petrol #Diesel #IMF

title: Ratusan CPNS yang Mengundurkan Diri Rugikan Negara dan Bisa Didenda Ratusan juta
description: Sebanyak 105 CPNS dilaporkan mengundurkan diri meski sudah lulus pada tahun 2021 lalu. Terkait hal ini, para peserta yang mengundurkan diri akan diberikan sanksi.|||Sanksi tersebut yakni peserta tidak boleh melamar pada penerimaan ASN periode berikutnya. title: Suzuki V-Strom 250 SX Review | Adventure Ready or A Comfortable Tourer?
description: One of the biggest surprise two-wheeler launches of 2022 is the Suzuki V-Strom 250 SX. The V-Strom SX is the first affordable ADV two-wheeler offering from the Japanese two-wheeler giant for the Indian market and also its third 250cc motorcycle. The Suzuki V-Strom SX is powered by the same 250cc engine as seen on its other 250cc siblings and even the gear ratios are identical. What is different though is the styling, the V-Strom 250 looks like a scaled-down version of the bigger V-Strom 1050 and the V-Strom 650.┬а|The new Suzuki 250cc ADV bike features LED headlight, all-digital instrument cluster with Bluetooth connectivity for navigation, call and message alerts and even an external USB charger. While the bike has the visual appeal of a proper adventure bike, the Suzuki V-Strom doesnтАЩt have the kit to justify the V-Strom name. The suspension travel is similar to its road-spec offerings and it doesnтАЩt even get dual-channel ABS. We head out for a 230km road trip from Dharamshala to Manali to find out if the V-Strom 250 SX is a proper adventure tourer or if it's just a sudo ADV bike.┬а|Host┬а - Arun Mohan Nadar|DOP - Neeraj Panwar|Editor - Harshvardhan Rathod|More details on the 2023 KTM 390 Duke - https://www.zigwheels.com/newbikes/Suzuki/v-strom-250┬а|DonтАЩt forget to also check out the following videos on ZigWheels:|Yamaha MT-15 Version 2.0 Road Test: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JorinтАж┬а|Royal Enfield Himalayan 450 Incoming: https://youtu.be/x89gE_8wUp0┬а|2022 KTM 390 Adventure Review: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H1fxUтАж┬а|Scram Attack - RE Scram 411 vs Yezdi Scrambler - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LtesldOMTI8

title: Anak Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Khan Mumtadz Hilang Teseret Arus Sungai di Swiss!
description: KOMPAS.TV - Anak sulung Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Khan Mumtadz atau biasa dipanggil Eril mengalami musibah di Bern, Swiss pada 26 Mei 2022 siang hari waktu Swiss.||||Musibah hilangnya anak sulung Ridwan Kamil tersebut terjadi saat Eril berenang di sungai Aaree, Bern bersama adik dan kawannya.||||Saat ingin naik ke permukaan, Eril terseret arus sungai yang cukup deras yang sebelumnya sempat mendapat bantuan dari kawannya.||||Kejadian tersebut terjadi pada tanggal 26 Mei 2022 siang hari waktu Swiss dengan kondisi cuaca cerah.||||Keluarga dari Ridwan Kamil sendiri saat itu sedang berada di Swiss untuk mencari sekolah untuk Eril yang akan melanjutkan ke jenjang S2.||||Saat kejadian, Pak Ridwan Kamil sedang berada di Inggris dalam kegiatan pemerintahan di luar negeri bersama delegasi dari Pemprov Jawa Barat. ||||----||||Jangan lewatkan streaming Kompas TV live 24 jam non stop di https://www.kompas.tv/live  agar kamu semua tidak ketinggalan berita-berita terkini, terlengkap, serta laporan langsung dari berbagai daerah di Indonesia.||||Subscribe juga channel YouTube Kompas TV  di https://www.youtube.com/c/kompastv dan aktifkan lonceng supaya kamu dapat notifikasi video terbaru langsung. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292998/anak-ridwan-kamil-emmeril-khan-mumtadz-hilang-teseret-arus-sungai-di-swiss

title: Kata Jokowi soal Kepemimpinan Gibran Rakabuming Raka sebagai Wali Kota Solo
description: SOLO, KOMPAS.TV  Presiden Joko Widodo tak berkomentar banyak soal sepak terjang anaknya Gibran Rakabuming Raka sebagai Wali Kota Solo.||||Hal ini disampaikan Jokowi saat kunjungan di Taman Kota Balekambang, Solo, Jawa Tengah pada Kamis (26/5)||||Presiden Jokowi mengaku sibuk karena pekerjaannya juga banyak sekali.||||"Waduh, saya enggak ngikuti. title: How 'Everything Everywhere All At Once' Pulled Off Its Kung Fu Fight Scenes | Movies Insider
description: The fight scenes in "Everything Everywhere All at Once" put a fresh spin on classic kung fu movies. We spoke with stunt coordinator Timothy Eulich and fight choreographers Andy and Brian Le about how the movie's most impressive action sequences came together.|Timothy, Andy, and Brian worked with directing duo Daniel Kwan and Daniel Scheinert, aka the Daniels, to plan and execute the film's fight scenes on a tight budget and shooting schedule, shooting almost entirely within the confines of a single warehouse building in Southern California. Here, they talk about the inspirations and references they pulled from in choreographing the action in "Everything Everywhere," from classic Hong Kong movies and Jackie Chan action flicks to break dancing and parkour. |Timothy has worked as a stunt coordinator and performer on TV series like "Westworld" and "Stranger Things" and films like "Spider-Man: No Way Home" and "Cobra Kai." Previously, he collaborated with the Daniels on their A24-released "Swiss Army Man," starring Paul Dano and Daniel Radcliffe.|Andy and Brian are the brothers and self-taught martial artists behind the popular YouTube channel Martial Club. They appear in several scenes of "Everything Everywhere" as both actors and stunt doubles, most memorably opposite Michelle Yeoh in the IRS trophy fight. Previously, the siblings worked on Marvel's "Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings," with Andy playing the Death Dealer in the film.|"Everything Everywhere All At Once" is out in theaters. title: Russia 'will not win' war in Ukraine, says German Chancellor Scholz | DW News
description: German Chancellor Scholz may have felt like he's the lonely leader of the West. Scholz delivered the closing address at the World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland, a meeting where the globe's economic and political leaders traditionally rub elbows, meet and greet. Not this year.|Scholz was the only leader of all the G-7 countries who traveled to Davos this year. And that jury is still on what being the only one means or symbolizes.  The world's leaders, especially in Europe and the US, are dealing with the war in Ukraine, broken global supply chains and soaring inflation.   |That didn't keep Ukrainian president Zelensky from zooming with the movers and shakers in Davos. title: Obesity and corporate greed | DW Documentary
description: Doctors predict that by 2030, half of the world's population will be overweight or obese. An epidemic of obesity is causing a rapid rise in diabetes, cardiovascular disease, and cancer. It's becoming the biggest health challenge worldwide.|Why has no country managed to stop this epidemic? The food industry and government authorities say it's due to a lack of individual self-discipline. Is this true? Or is it the result of collective failure -- a symptom of a liberal society that abhors obesity, yet produces people who are overweight. Is society itself to blame for this situation?|Around the world, politicians, priests, doctors, and average people are standing up to multinational food corporations. They want to take back control of their nutrition and their bodies -- and they're using the law, scientific evidence, and political activism to correct the claim that people who are obese have only themselves to blame. These critics focus on sugary drinks that can be as addictive as some hard drugs; misleading advertising directed at children and low-income people; governments that turn a blind eye to junk-food companies; and lobbying that pushes the limits of legality.|These people say that a "hostile takeover" of our food has been |underway for four decades, and they're demanding new legislation to put a stop to it. This documentary investigates how Chile is leading the way in this struggle. Which country will be the next to confront the big food corporations in the name of public health?|#documentary #dwdocumentary #obesity|______|DW Documentary gives you knowledge beyond the headlines. googling with these keywords: |- Continental drift: An early theory of land movement that posited that the continents floated on the ocean bed. |- Tetrahedral hypothesis: An early theory that attempted to explain the arrangement of EarthтАЩs continents and oceans based on the geometry of a tetrahedron.|- Plate tectonics: The generally accepted theory that the EarthтАЩs surface is made up title: PM Modi dedicates to the nation and lays foundation stone of development initiatives in Chennai
description: PM in Chennai|In a step towards boosting infrastructure development, enhancing connectivity and giving an impetus to ease of living in the region, Prime Minister will dedicate to the nation and lay the foundation stone of 11 projects worth over Rs 31,500 crore in Chennai. These projects will also help significantly improve socio-economic prosperity in the region, have a transformative impact on several sectors and also help create employment opportunities.|In Chennai, Prime Minister will dedicate to the nation five projects worth over Rs 2960 crore. The 75 km long Madurai-Teni (Railway Gauge Conversion Project), built at a project cost of over Rs. 500 crore, will facilitate access and give a boost to tourism in the region. The 30 km long third railway line between Tambaram - Chengalpattu, built at a project cost of over Rs. 590 crore, will facilitate running of more Suburban services, thus offering greater options and enhancing comfort for the travellers.|The 115 km long Ennore-Chengalpattu section and 271 km long Thiruvallur-Bengaluru section of ETBPNMT natural gas pipeline, built at a project cost of around Rs. 850 crore and Rs 910 crore respectively, will facilitate supply of natural gas to consumers as well industries in Tamil Nadu, Karnataka and Andhra Pradesh.|The programme will also witness inauguration of 1152 houses constructed as part of Light House Project - Chennai, built at a cost of Rs 116 crore under Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana-Urban.|Prime Minister will also lay the foundation stone of six projects, being built at a cost of over Rs. 28,540 crore.|The 262 Km long Bengaluru - Chennai Expressway will be built at a cost of over Rs. 14,870 crore. It will pass-through states of Karnataka, Andhra Pradesh and Tamil Nadu and help reduce travel time between Bengaluru and Chennai by 2-3 hours. The 4 Lane double decker elevated road connecting Chennai Port to Maduravoyal (NH-4), of about 21 Km in length, will be built at a cost of over Rs 5850 crore. It will facilitate round the clock approach of goods vehicles to Chennai port. The тАЛтАЛ94 km long 4 lane Neraluru to Dharmapuri section of NH-844 and 31 km long 2 lane with paved shoulders of Meensurutti to Chidambaram section of NH-227, being built at a cost of around Rs 3870 crore and Rs 720 respectively, will help provide seamless connectivity in the region.|The foundation stones for redevelopment of five Railway stations: Chennai Egmore, Rameswaram, Madurai, Katpadi and Kanniyakumari, will also be laid during the programme. This project will be completed at a cost of over Rs. 1800 crore, and is being undertaken with a view to enhance convenience and comfort of the passengers through provision of modern amenities.|Prime Minister will also lay the foundation stone of a Multi Modal Logistic Park at Chennai worth around Rs. 1430 crore. It will provide seamless intermodal freight movement and also offer multiple functionalities.|Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/8qsb5E Stay Updated! title: Bilanzen pr├╝fen und Firmen durchleuchten: Was verdient ein Wirtschaftspr├╝fer? | Lohnt sich das? | BR
description: Jakob Eisenreich ist ein Meister der Kennziffern und Bilanzen. Als Wirtschaftspr├╝fer hat er die Zahlen von Unternehmen im Blick тАУ sei es, wenn ein Jahresabschluss gepr├╝ft oder eine Firmen├╝bernahme begleitet wird. Es ist ein Job mit einem sehr guten Verdienst, aber auch mit viel Verantwortung. Stichwort: Bilanzskandal um Wirecard тАУ es kann also einiges schiefgehen, wenn unsauber gearbeitet wird.|Der 35-J├дhrige arbeitet f├╝r Leidel & Partner in Regen im Bayerischen Wald. Die Kanzlei bietet neben Wirtschaftspr├╝fung auch noch andere Dienstleistungen wie Steuerberatung oder Rechtsbeistand. Jakob ist dort 2018 Jahren als Partner eingestiegen (zun├дchst als Juniorpartner). Er zahlt deshalb noch bis 2030 einen Existenzgr├╝nderkredit an die Bank ab. Was er aus seiner T├дtigkeit als Steuerberater verdient, gibt er 1 zu 1 an die Bank wegen des Kredits weiter.|Dieser finanzielle Posten ist deshalb nicht Teil unseres Films. Wir wollen nur das Gehalt als Wirtschaftspr├╝fer zeigen. Klar ist aber nat├╝rlich auch: Wenn er den Kredit irgendwann abbezahlt hat, wird sein Verdienst h├╢her ausfallen. Mehr dazu findet ihr wie immer im angepinnten Kommentar. |Als Wirtschaftspr├╝fer hat Jakob viele Mandaten in der Region, manche betreut die Kanzlei seit Jahrzehnten. Zugleich versucht er auch immer wieder, Neukunden zu gewinnen. Eine der Kernaufgaben des Jobs ist die betriebswirtschaftliche Pr├╝fung von Jahresabschl├╝ssen. Denn ab einer gewissen Gr├╢├Яe sind Unternehmen dazu verpflichtet, ihre Bilanz extern durchleuchten zu lassen тАУ damit auch tats├дchlich alles so stimmt wie angegeben. Das Prinzip dahinter: Die Unternehmen haben eine Verantwortung gegen├╝ber anderen Firmen, Angestellten, usw., die auf korrekt angegebene Finanzen angewiesen sind.|Neben der reinen Wirtschaftspr├╝fung k├╝mmert sich Jakob mit seinem Team auch h├дufig um sogenannte pr├╝fungsnahe Beratungen. Dabei betreut er einen Unternehmensverkauf oder -kauf aus finanzwirtschaftlicher Sicht und gibt seinen Mandaten wichtige Hinweise, ob er aus finanzieller Sicht von einem Gesch├дft abraten oder es bef├╝rworten w├╝rde. |Als dritte Aufgabe ├╝bernimmt Jakob au├Яerdem sogenannte Schiedsgutachten. Das hei├Яt, er wird von einer externen Stelle als neutrale Partei beauftragt, sich z.B. Unternehmen, Anteile oder wirtschaftliche Handlungen eines Gesch├дftsf├╝hrers genauer anzusehen. Seine Gutachten k├╢nnen dann auch Grundlage vor Gericht sein, etwa bei familien-, zivil-, oder erbrechtlichen F├дllen.|Wir begleiten Jakob an einem typischen Arbeitstag: Unter anderem beginnt er mit seinem Team eine Wirtschaftspr├╝fung bei einem typischen Mittelst├дndler, eine interne Besprechung zu einem laufenden Projekten offenbart wenig Gutes тАУ und Jakob versucht einen neuen Mandaten f├╝r die Kanzlei zu gewinnen. Ob das klappt?|---|Das ist тАЮLohnt sich das?тАЬ: |Ein Mensch, ein Job, ein Leben. Und am Ende die Frage: Lohnt sich das? Wir begleiten Menschen in ihrem Beruf und zeigen ihr Leben. Rentiert es sich f├╝r das Gehalt zu arbeiten und damit das eigene Leben zu finanzieren? Was macht mich an der Arbeit gl├╝cklich? Wir vergleichen nicht nur Geh├дlter, sondern zeigen wie Menschen von ihrer Arbeit leben. |Wir sind immer auf der Suche nach Protagonisten: Wenn ihr auch zeigen wollt, wie ihr mit eurem Job lebt, k├╢nnt ihr gerne an lohntsichdas@br.de schreiben!|In eigener Sache: Auch wir sind nicht unfehlbar тАУ und obwohl wir uns gr├╢├Яte M├╝he geben, jede individuelle, finanzielle Lebenssituation anschaulich, korrekt und verst├дndlich darzustellen, brauchen wir manchmal Hilfe. Hierbei unterst├╝tzt uns immer wieder kompetent der Landesverband der steuerberatenden und wirtschaftspr├╝fenden Berufe in Bayern e. V. тАУ vielen Dank daf├╝r!|Autorin: Tobias Brunner|Kamera: Jasper Br├╝ggemann|Schnitt: Moritz Mayer|CvD: Benedikt Angermeier|Redaktion: Eva Limmer, Manuela Baldauf

title: Judenhass: Die lange Geschichte
description: Was kommt euch beim Wort тАЮAntisemitismusтАЭ als Erstes in den Sinn? Der Anschlag auf die Synagoge in Halle (Saale) 2019? Oder der Holocaust bzw. die Shoa an den europ├дischen Juden im Nationalsozialismus unter Adolf Hitler? |Der Antisemitismus, also der Hass auf Juden, ist schon Jahrtausende alt. Beispielsweise  beschuldigen die ersten Christen pauschal das Judentum der Ermordung Jesu Christi. Diese Vorurteile und der Antijudaismus halten sich ├╝ber die Jahrhunderte, werden sogar immer weiter gesch├╝rt. Besonders in Krisenzeiten m├╝ssen Juden zu Unrecht immer wieder als S├╝ndenb├╢cke f├╝r Naturkatastrophen, Krankheiten wie die Pest oder verlorene Kriege herhalten. Juden werden von der christlichen Mehrheitsgesellschaft in Europa vertrieben, ausgegrenzt und systematisch diskriminiert. Oft schl├дgt der Hass auch in Gewalt um. Es kommt zu Pogromen, bei denen Jagd auf j├╝dische Menschen gemacht wird. title: La bestia nera тАУ Report 23/05/2022
description: https://www.raiplay.it/programmi/report - Di Paolo Mondani, da Report del 23/05/2022. A 30 anni dalla morte di Giovanni Falcone, emergono documenti e protagonisti dimenticati in grado di gettare una nuova luce su quei fatti. A Capaci, Cosa Nostra non ha agito da sola: estremisti di destra e uomini di mafia, secondo testimoni e documenti ritrovati, sarebbero stati di nuovo insieme, dopo gli anni della strategia della tensione, in un abbraccio mortale costato la vita ai giudici Falcone e Borsellino. I due magistrati avevano il quadro completo, e oggi, tornando ad ascoltare collaboratori ed ex carabinieri, Report prova a ricostruirlo.

title: China bridge row: Indian army counters XiтАЩs threat along LAC; Steps up military deployment
description: While China builds a second, bigger and broader bridge over the Pangong Tso, Hindustan Times has learnt that the Indian army has been deployed at the LAC to counter PeopleтАЩs Liberation Army's aggressive infrastructure development. This comes nearly a month after the new Chief of Army Staff, General Manoj Pande, conducted a security review of the Chinese PLAтАЩs positions in East Ladakh. As per HT report, the Indian Army has studied the satellite pictures of the twin Chinese bridges and found out that the first bridge built over the narrowest part of Pangong Tso at Khurnak Fort was 6m  wide. The second bridge is 11m wide and has the capacity to handle 70 tons of load, which is more than the weight of the heaviest Chinese tank. title: Momen Adik Jokowi dan Anwar Usman Bernyanyi Bareng Judika di Pelaminan
description: SOLO, KOMPAS.TV - Pernikahan adik kandung Presiden Joko Widodo, Idayati dengan Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi RI Anwar Usman berlangsung di Gedung Graha Saba Buana, Solo, Jawa Tengah, Kamis (26/5).||||Dalam acara resepsi, hadir sebagai penghibur penyanyi Judika.||||Pada kesempatan itu, tampak Idayati dan sang suami Anwar Usman bernyanyi bersama Judika di pelaminan.||||Idayati yang mengenakan gaun pengantin berwarna merah itu tampak menikmati alunan musik yang mengiringinya.||||Tak hanya Idayati, sang suami Anwar Usman turut mempersembahkan lagu untuk istri tercintanya.||||Baca Juga Momen Tamu VIP Kabinet Indonesia Maju Berdatangan ke Pernikahan Adik Jokowi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292744/momen-tamu-vip-kabinet-indonesia-maju-berdatangan-ke-pernikahan-adik-jokowi||||Judika pun memuji kepiawaian Ketua MK itu dalam tarik suara. "aslinya penyanyi ternyata" kata Judika.||||Untuk diketahui, adik kandung Presiden Joko Widodo (Jokowi) dan Ketua Mahkamah Agung Anwar Usman resmi menikah, pada Kamis (26/5) di Gedung Graha Saba Buana, Solo, Jawa Tengah.||||Wali nikah pernikahan tersebut ialah Presiden Joko Widodo selaku kakak kandung Idayati.||||Sementara Wakil Presiden Maruf Amin dan Panglima TNI Jenderal Andika Perkasa menjadi saksi pernikahan.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292877/momen-adik-jokowi-dan-anwar-usman-bernyanyi-bareng-judika-di-pelaminan

title: Indian Navy hits 'bulls eye' from warship INS Teg; Surface-to-air missile system tested
description: The Indian Navy's guided-missile anti-submarine stealth frigate successfully engaged a low flying target with its surface-to-air missile (SAM) system. As per reports, the test fire took place from Talwar Class Indian Navy warship - INS Teg. The location of the test firing was not shared. "All in a days work! Watch YourNavy's guided-missile anti-submarine stealth frigate do what it does best - successfully engage a low flying target with its SAM system, reaffirming the mantra of her crew, HIT FIRST! HIT HARD! Congrats to the team for a text book bullseye!" the Indian Navy tweeted. title: Momen Presiden Jokowi jadi Wali Nikah Adiknya dengan Anwar Usman
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV -  Adik Presiden Jokowi, Idayati menikah dengan Ketua MK Anwar Usman. ||||Keduanya telah melangsungkan pernikahan di Graha Saba Buana Solo Kamis (26/5/2022).||||Baca Juga Momen Tamu VIP Kabinet Indonesia Maju Berdatangan ke Pernikahan Adik Jokowi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292744/momen-tamu-vip-kabinet-indonesia-maju-berdatangan-ke-pernikahan-adik-jokowi||||"Haji anwar usman SH.MH, bin haji Suman, saya nikahkan dan saya jodohkan dengan saudari perempuan saya Idayati binti Notomiharjo nikah dengan engkau, dengan mas kawin, dengan seperangkat alat salat dan sebuah jam tangan dibayar tunai."ucap Jokowi saat menjadi wali nikah keduanya, Kamis (26/5/2022). ||||"Saya terima nikah dan jodohnya idayati binti Notomiharjo dengan mahar tersebut tunai," jawab Anwar Usman.||||Adapun saksi nikah yang dihadirkan ialah Wakil Presiden Ma'ruf Amin dari pihak perempuan dan Andika menjadi saksi nikah dari pihak laki-laki.||||Video Editor: Febi||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292764/momen-presiden-jokowi-jadi-wali-nikah-adiknya-dengan-anwar-usman

title: KIsah Cinta Ketua MK dan Adik Jokowi yang Berakhir Bahagia di Pelaminan!
description: KOMPAS.TV - Sejak masih berupa isu dan rencana hingga hari-H, pernikahan Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi, Anwar Usman dan adik Presiden Joko Widodo, Idayati selalu hangat diperbincangkan publik.||||Tak ada ritual pingitan yang dijalani Anwar Usman dan Idayati, seperti pasangan calon pengantin Jawa pada umumnya.||||Dengan jadwal yang padat, Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi dan adik Presiden Joko Widodo ini justru seharian menghabiskan waktu bersama menjelang pernikahan mereka.||||Rabu (25/5/2022) pagi, keduanya menggelar acara pengajian bersama-sama di rumah almarhumah ibunda Jokowi dan Idayati, Sujiatmi Notomiharjo di Solo, Jawa Tengah.||||Baca Juga Usai Hadiri Nikahan Adik, Jokowi Blusukan ke Taman Balekambang dan Pasar Mojosongo di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292789/usai-hadiri-nikahan-adik-jokowi-blusukan-ke-taman-balekambang-dan-pasar-mojosongo||||Rabu (25/5/2022) sore, Anwar dan Idayati juga hadir langsung dalam acara gladi bersih prosesi pernikahan keduanya.||||Siapapun yang hadir di Graha Saba Buana sore itu, pasti bisa melihat binar mata penuh cinta dan bahagia yang terpancar dari raut wajah mereka.||||Di balik segala kontroversinya, pihak keluarga tetap mendukung keputusan Anwar untuk mempersunting Idayati.||||Ketulusan cinta Anwar Usman kepada Idayati juga dirasakan oleh Wedding Organizer yang membidani acara pernikahan ini.||||Tak banyak pasangan berusia lanjut yang begitu mantap melanjutkan ke jenjang pernikahan, memutuskan hidup bersama sambil mengasuh anak cucu mereka.||||Selamat menempuh hidup baru Ibu Idayati dan Pak Anwar Usman,||semoga selalu langgeng dan berbahagia.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292795/kisah-cinta-ketua-mk-dan-adik-jokowi-yang-berakhir-bahagia-di-pelaminan

title: Suzuki Vision Gran Turismo : Unveiled

title: Werbeverbot f├╝r Schwangerschaftsabbr├╝che abschaffen?| Markus Lanz vom 25. Mai 2022
description: Der Paragraf 219a, Werbeverbot f├╝r einen Schwangerschaftsabbruch. Dieser Paragraf wird immer h├дufiger in der ├╢ffentlichen Debatte stark diskutiert und auch in der aktuellen Politik fordern viele Politikerinnen und Politiker die Abschaffung dieses Paragrafen. Doch es gibt auch viele Gegenstimmen, die bei der Diskussion um Paragrafen 219a nur eine Scheindebatte sehen, denn in Wahrheit ginge es den Gegner*innen um den eigentlichen Paragrafen 218, dem wirklichen Verbot eines Schwangerschaftsabbruches.|F├╝r die Abschaffung des Paragrafen 219a ist die Gyn├дkologin Alicia Baier, die sich seit Jahren durch ihre Arbeit intensiv mit dem Thema besch├дftigt. Sie verstehe bis heute noch nicht, warum sie zwar auf ihrer Website sagen darf, dass sie Schwangerschaftsabbr├╝che durchf├╝hrt, aber den Frauen nicht erkl├дren kann, wie sie diese durchf├╝hrt. An diesem Punkt w├дren die betroffenen Frauen komplett auf sich allein gestellt, was sie nur umso mehr verunsichert. ├Дrztinnen und ├Дrzten sei es ohnehin verboten, Werbung f├╝r Anbieter medizinischer Ausr├╝stung, Medikamenten und Co. zu machen, daher h├дtte der Paragraf 219a so oder so schon einen Punkt, der seine N├╢tigkeit infrage stellt. |Klar gegen die Abschaffung dieses Paragrafen stellt sich die Bayerische Staatsministerin f├╝r Familie, Arbeit und Soziales Ulrike Scharf von der CSU. F├╝r sie sei der Aspekt wichtig, dass man zwei rechtliche Aspekte in dieser  Debatte immer mit einbeziehen m├╝sse: Das Lebensrecht des Kindes und das Selbstbestimmungsrecht der werdenden Mutter. Diese sind rechtlich festgeschrieben, weshalb man einen Schwangerschaftsabbruch gesondert betrachten sollte. Au├Яerdem gebe es schon Aufkl├дrungsangebote, die man als Frau nutzen k├╢nne.|Den gesamten Talk findet ihr hier: https://kurz.zdf.de/AT6i/| |Weitere G├дste in der Sendung:|Karl Lauterbach, Politiker|Der Bundesgesundheitsminister (SPD) ├дu├Яert sich zum Ausbruch der Affenpocken, seinem Pandemie-Management und zur erwarteten Corona-Entwicklung im Herbst.| |Mariam Lau, Journalistin|Die тАЮZeitтАЬ-Politikredakteurin bilanziert Lauterbachs erste Monate als Bundesgesundheitsminister. Zudem analysiert sie das Zusammenwirken der Ampel-Koalition├дre. |_____|Hier auf ZDFheute Nachrichten erfahrt ihr, was auf der Welt passiert und was uns alle etwas angeht: Wir sorgen f├╝r Durchblick in der Nachrichtenwelt, erkl├дren die Hintergr├╝nde und gehen auf gesellschaftliche Debatten ein. Diskutiert in Livestreams mit uns und bildet euch eure eigene Meinung mit den Fakten, die wir euch pr├дsentieren.|Abonniert unseren Kanal, um nichts mehr zu verpassen.|Immer auf dem aktuellen Stand seid ihr auf http://www.ZDFheute.de/.|#┬з219a #┬з218 #Schwangerschaftsabbruch

title: 'I believe the PM has lied repeatedly, knowingly' says Chair of Commons Standards Committee
description: Chair of Commons Standards Committee Chris Bryant has said he believes the Prime Minister "has lied repeatedly" and "knowingly", following the publication of a report into lockdown-breaking parties at Downing Street. |Mr Bryant said "the lockdown rules didn't say anywhere about work events, they simply said no gatherings were allowed, and these were gatherings and the PM was at them."|Mr Bryant has recused himself from the Commons Standards Committee, which could call for the Prime Minister's suspension from the House from anywhere between "one and ten days" should they find he mislead parliament.|#Partygate #BorisJohnson #SkyNews|SUBSCRIBE to our YouTube channel for more videos: http://www.youtube.com/skynews |Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/skynews |Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/skynews |Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/skynews |Follow us on TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@skynews|For more content go to http://news.sky.com and download our apps: |Apple: https://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/sky-news/id316391924?mt=8 |Android https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bskyb.skynews.android&hl=en_GB |Sky News videos are now available in Spanish here/Los video de Sky News est├бn disponibles en espa├▒ol aqu├н https://www.youtube.com/channel/skynewsespanol|Sky News videos are also available in German here/Hier k├╢nnen Sie au├Яerdem Sky News-Videos auf Deutsch finden: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHYg31l2xrF-Bj859nsOfnA|To enquire about licensing Sky News content, you can find more information here:  https://news.sky.com/info/library-sales

title: Bukan Tokoh Politik, Ini Mak Comblang Sang Ketua MK dan Adik Presiden Jokowi
description: SOLO, KOMPAS.TV - Di balik segala kontroversinya, pihak keluarga tetap mendukung keputusan Anwar untuk mempersunting Idayati.||||Meski kisah asmara mereka bergerak begitu cepat dalam senyap menuju jenjang pernikahan, ternyata ada sosok mak comblang penting yang mempertemukan keduanya pada Oktober 2021 lalu.||||Ketulusan cinta Anwar Usman kepada Idayati, juga dirasakan oleh "wedding organizer" yang membidangi acara pernikahan ini.||||Tak banyak pasangan berusia lanjut yang begitu mantap melanjutkan ke jenjang pernikahan memutuskan hidup bersama sambil mengasuh anak cucu mereka.||||Anwar Usman menjadi duda setelah ditinggal sang istri, Suhada Binti Ahmad Sidik yang wafat karena sakit pada Februari 2021 lalu.||||Sementara Idayati, juga ditinggal wafat suaminya, Hari Mulyono sejak 2018.||||Dari pernikahan sebelumnya, Anwar memiliki tiga orang anak, sementara Idayati punya dua orang anak yang kini masing-masing juga sudah berkeluarga.||||Pada Haro Kamis, 26 Mei 2022 Gedung Graha Saba Buana sekali lagi menjadi saksi bisu momen sakral pernikahan keluarga Presiden Joko Widodo.||||Ada 200 tamu akad nikah serta 800 orang tamu resepsi yang dijaga ketat oleh lebih dari dua ribu personel gabungan TNI dan Polisi.||||Selamat menempuh hidup baru,  Ibu Idayati dan Pak Anwar Usman.||||Semoga selalu langgeng dan berbahagia. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292755/bukan-tokoh-politik-ini-mak-comblang-sang-ketua-mk-dan-adik-presiden-jokowi

title: Yunarto: Presiden Membuka Ruang Komunikasi Dengan Tema Yang Jelas - SATU MEJA
description: OMPASTV - Presiden Jokowi dianggap memberi sinyal dukungan untuk Ganjar Pranowo. Kode itu dilempar Jokowi dalam acara Rakernas V Projo. Kalimat "mungkin yang kita dukung ada di sini" dianggap sebagai restu dan dukungan Jokowi untuk gubernur Jawa Tengah ini.||||Ganjar memang digadang-gadang menjadi salah satu calon yang berpeluang maju di Pemilihan Presiden (Pilpres) 2024 mendatang. Meski belum direstui PDIP, hasil survei berbagai lembaga terkait bursa capres menempatkan Ganjar sebagai salah satu tokoh dengan elektabilitas tertinggi selain Prabowo Subianto.||||Benarkah Jokowi mendukung Ganjar Pranowo untuk maju di Pilpres 2024 nanti? Lalu bagaimana PDI Perjuangan menyikapi manuver Jokowi ini? Saksikan talkshow Satu Meja The Forum "MEMBACA SINYAL JOKOWI" Rabu, 25 Mei 2022 pukul 20.30 WIB di Kompas TV bersama jurnalis senior Harian Kompas, Budiman Tanuredjo.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292750/yunarto-presiden-membuka-ruang-komunikasi-dengan-tema-yang-jelas-satu-meja

title: Jazilul Fawaid: Elektoral Ganjar Yang Tinggi Karena Ada Jokowi - SATU MEJA
description: KOMPASTV - Presiden Jokowi dianggap memberi sinyal dukungan untuk Ganjar Pranowo. Kode itu dilempar Jokowi dalam acara Rakernas V Projo. Kalimat "mungkin yang kita dukung ada di sini" dianggap sebagai restu dan dukungan Jokowi untuk gubernur Jawa Tengah ini.||||Ganjar memang digadang-gadang menjadi salah satu calon yang berpeluang maju di Pemilihan Presiden (Pilpres) 2024 mendatang. Meski belum direstui PDIP, hasil survei berbagai lembaga terkait bursa capres menempatkan Ganjar sebagai salah satu tokoh dengan elektabilitas tertinggi selain Prabowo Subianto.||||Benarkah Jokowi mendukung Ganjar Pranowo untuk maju di Pilpres 2024 nanti? Lalu bagaimana PDI Perjuangan menyikapi manuver Jokowi ini? Saksikan talkshow Satu Meja The Forum "MEMBACA SINYAL JOKOWI" Rabu, 25 Mei 2022 pukul 20.30 WIB di Kompas TV bersama jurnalis senior Harian Kompas, Budiman Tanuredjo.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292751/jazilul-fawaid-elektoral-ganjar-yang-tinggi-karena-ada-jokowi-satu-meja

title: Membaca Sinyal Jokowi - SATU MEJA
description: KOMPASTV - Presiden Jokowi dianggap memberi sinyal dukungan untuk Ganjar Pranowo. Kode itu dilempar Jokowi dalam acara Rakernas V Projo. Kalimat "mungkin yang kita dukung ada di sini" dianggap sebagai restu dan dukungan Jokowi untuk gubernur Jawa Tengah ini.||||Ganjar memang digadang-gadang menjadi salah satu calon yang berpeluang maju di Pemilihan Presiden (Pilpres) 2024 mendatang. Meski belum direstui PDIP, hasil survei berbagai lembaga terkait bursa capres menempatkan Ganjar sebagai salah satu tokoh dengan elektabilitas tertinggi selain Prabowo Subianto.||||Benarkah Jokowi mendukung Ganjar Pranowo untuk maju di Pilpres 2024 nanti? Lalu bagaimana PDI Perjuangan menyikapi manuver Jokowi ini? Saksikan talkshow Satu Meja The Forum "MEMBACA SINYAL JOKOWI" Rabu, 25 Mei 2022 pukul 20.30 WIB di Kompas TV bersama jurnalis senior Harian Kompas, Budiman Tanuredjo.|||| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292748/membaca-sinyal-jokowi-satu-meja

title: Fakta Menarik Tempat Pernikahan Adik Jokowi dan Ketua MK Anwar Usman
description: KOMPAS.TV- Pernikahan Idayati dan Anwar Usman berlangsung di Gedung Graha Saba Buana, Sumber, Banjarsari, Kota Surakarta, Jawa Tengah.||||Ternyata tempat pernikahan adik Jokowi dan Ketua MK ini menyimpan sederet fakta menarik, apa saja?||||Menyadur dari Kompas.tv berikut informasinya:||||Nama Graha Saba Buana||||Nama Graha Saba Buana mempunyai arti khusus pada kata terakhirnya yakni Buana.||||Kata ini gabungan dari dua suku kata yakni bu, dan ana ana sendiri merupakan kependekan dari Iriana.||||Hadiah Ulang Tahun dari Jokowi untuk Iriana||||Gedung ini diberikan tahun 2002 untuk kegiatan Iriana saat ditinggal Jokowi bertugas.||||Daya Tampung Graha Saba Buana||||Gedung ini seluas 4000m persegi dan mampu menampung 2000 orang sementara untuk kendaraan dapat memuat sekiranya 300 mobil.||||Desain Interior Klasik||||Graha Saba Buana berdesain interior unik dengan nuansa Jawa Klasik yang kental.||||Diskon Khusus Tetangga||||Diskon yang diberikan sebesar 20% , namun diskon ini hanya untuk tetangga satu RT dengan Jokowi.||||Baca Juga Momen Tamu VIP Kabinet Indonesia Maju Berdatangan ke Pernikahan Adik Jokowi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292744/momen-tamu-vip-kabinet-indonesia-maju-berdatangan-ke-pernikahan-adik-jokowi||||Editor Video & Grafis: Arief Rahman ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292813/fakta-menarik-tempat-pernikahan-adik-jokowi-dan-ketua-mk-anwar-usman

title: Andika Perkasa Angkat Bicara Soal Namanya Diduetkan Bareng Ganjar Pranowo di 2024
description: SLEMAN, KOMPAS.TV - Panglima TNI Jenderal Andika Perkasa angkat bicara soal namanya yang diduetkan dengan Ganjar Pranowo untuk Pilpres 2024.||||Menanggapi hal itu, Andika mengucapkan terima kasih atas dukungan yang diberikan banyak pihak. Andika menyebut dukungan itu sebagai bentuk kepercayaan dari banyak orang, baik untuk pribadinya maupun institusi TNI.||||Namun Andika menegaskan saat ini dirinya akan fokus bekerja sebagai panglima TNI terlebih dahulu hingga masa jabatannya selesai.||||Baca Juga Andika Perkasa Ungkap Anggota TNI Terlibat Kasus Kerangkeng Manusia di Langkat Bisa Bertambah di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292716/andika-perkasa-ungkap-anggota-tni-terlibat-kasus-kerangkeng-manusia-di-langkat-bisa-bertambah||||Diketahui, nama Panglima TNI Jendral Andika Perkasa menjadi salah satu yang disebut-sebut layak diduetkan dengan Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo dalam pemilu Presiden 2024 mendatang.||||Bahkan di Yogyakarta muncul sekelompok orang yang mengatasnamakan relawan Ganjar-Perkasa.||||Terkait munculnya relawan Ganjar-Perkasa ini, Andika pun mengaku belum pernah dipertemukan secara khusus dengan Ganjar untuk membicarakan duet calon pada pemilu Presiden 2024 mendatang.||||Video Editor: Ian Andrian||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292754/andika-perkasa-angkat-bicara-soal-namanya-diduetkan-bareng-ganjar-pranowo-di-2024

title: SAH! Ketua MK Anwar Usman Resmi Jadi Suami Idayati, Adik Presiden Jokowi
description: SOLO, KOMPAS.TV - Akad nikah adik Presiden Joko Widodo, Idayati dengan Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi, Anwar Usman berlangsung khidmat.||||Ijab qobul, Idayati dan Anwar Usman berlangsung pukul 10.00 pagi tadi di Graha Saba Buana, Banjarsari, Solo, Jawa Tengah.||||Rangkaian prosesi akad nikah sebelumnya diiringi alunan gamelan di gedung yang didekorasi dengan nuansa Jawa klasik.||||Baca Juga Usung Adat Jawa Klasik, Ini Makna Dekorasi Pelaminan Adik Jokowi dan Ketua MK di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292757/usung-adat-jawa-klasik-ini-makna-dekorasi-pelaminan-adik-jokowi-dan-ketua-mk||||Sejak Kamis (26/5/2022) pagi, sesuai adat tradisi Jawa, tahap pertama dilakukan prosesi pasrah tampi atau menyerahkan mempelai laki-laki kepada keluarga mempelai perempuan.||||Setelah diterima oleh keluarga mempelai perempuan, mempelai laki-laki langsung ke meja akad nikah, Presiden Jokowi sebagai wali nikah mempelai perempuan dan berlaku sebagai saksi Panglima TNI Jendral Andhika Perkasa dan Wakil Presiden, Ma'ruf Amin.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292767/sah-ketua-mk-anwar-usman-resmi-jadi-suami-idayati-adik-presiden-jokowi

title: Siapa Sebenarnya Idayati Adik Presiden Jokowi dan Anwar Usman Ketua MK yang Menikah? Ini Profilnya
description: KOMPAS.TV - Adik Presiden Joko Widodo, Idayati, Kamis 26 Mei 2022 dipersunting oleh Anwar Usman yang merupakan Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi.||||Surakarta Jawa Tengah dipilih menjadi tempat akad nikah dan resepsi.||||Idayati adalah adik kedua Jokowi yang lahir pada 26 Mei 1966 di Solo Jawa Tengah.||||Ia memiliki dua anak dari pernikahan pertamanya, yaitu Septiara Silvani Putri dan Rimbo Galih Samudra.||||Sehari-hari ia merupakan ibu rumah tangga dan menetap di Solo||||Lalu siapakah sosok Anwar Usman yang mempersunting adik orang nomor satu di Indonesia ini?||||Mengutip Laman Mahkamah Konstitusi  Anwar lahir dan dibesarkan di Desa Rasabou, Kecamatan Bolo, Bima, Nusa Tenggara Barat.||||Pria kelahiran 65 tahun silam itu mengawali kariernya sebagai guru honorer pada 1975.||||Setelah lulus dari SDN 03 Sil, Bima pada tahun 1969, ia melanjutkan pendidikannya di Sekolah Pendidikan Guru Agama Negeri atau PGAN selama enam tahun hingga 1975.||||Pada perjalanan kariernya di lembaga peradilan Anwar Usman sempat menjabat sebagai Wakil Ketua MK untuk dua periode.||||Selepas itu, Usman juga diangkat menjadi Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi dengan masa jabatan dua periode.||||Periode pertama pada 6 April 2011-6 April 2016 dan periode kedua 6 April 2016-6 April 2026. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292721/siapa-sebenarnya-idayati-adik-presiden-jokowi-dan-anwar-usman-ketua-mk-yang-menikah-ini-profilnya

title: Global National: May 25, 2022 | Agony and anger rise in aftermath of Uvalde, Texas school shooting
description: The city of Uvalde, Texas is in despair after a gunman shot and killed 19 children and two teachers, in what is now the second deadliest U.S. school shooting. Jackson Proskow reports on who the victims are, the devastating grief overwhelming their families, and the anger politicians are facing once again over another senseless mass shooting.|The school shooting is also forcing many people to revisit America's past school shootings, especially the December 2012 massacre at Sandy Hook Elementary School. While it and every other mass shooting has spawned calls for tighter gun control in the U.S., Eric Sorensen explains how gun reform has been an uphill battle.|As Ottawa cleans up from a vicious storm, now volunteers are doing what they can to help residents left in the dark. David Akin visits some of the hardest-hit neighbourhoods in the nation's capital to see how people are coping.|Concerns are growing about the global outbreak of the monkeypox virus, as more cases are confirmed in Canada. Dan Spector looks at where infections are being detected, the push for vaccinations, and how health experts are urging calm.|In the U.K., a critical independent report has been released on British Prime Minister Boris Johnson's multiple boozy parties which broke pandemic rules. title: Boeing #Starliner Spacecraft Deorbit Burn and Landing (Official NASA Broadcast)
description: Watch the landing of Boeing's uncrewed Starliner, targeted at 6:49 p.m. EDT (22:49 UTC) at White Sands Space Harbor at the U.S. ArmyтАЩs White Sands Missile Range in New Mexico. This return to Earth will wrap up the six-day Orbital Flight Test-2, which will provide valuable data toward NASA certifying BoeingтАЩs crew transportation system for regular flights with astronauts to and from the International Space Station.  |Boeing's Starliner launched to the space station on Thursday, May 19 aboard a United Launch Alliance Atlas V rocket, and docked to the orbiting laboratory on Friday, May 20. The crew opened Starliner's hatch on Saturday, May 21. The spacecraft will return home with more than 600 pounds of cargo, including Nitrogen Oxygen Recharge System reusable tanks that provide breathable air to station crew members. The tanks will be refurbished on Earth and sent back to station on a future flight.|Image Credit: ESA/NASA

title: Droht ein Atomwaffeneinsatz? Claudia Major und Frederik Pleitgen im Gespr├дch | maischberger
description: Erbitterte K├дmpfe in der Ost-Ukraine, aber keine Feuerpause ist derzeit in Sicht. Wie lange wird dieser Krieg noch dauern? Dar├╝ber diskutieren bei maischberger die Sicherheitsexpertin Claudia Major und der CNN-Journalist Frederik Pleitgen. |Dieser Krieg werde noch l├дnger andauern, erkl├дrte Claudia Major im Gespr├дch mit Sandra Maischberger und Frederik Pleitgen. Selbst wenn es jetzt Angebote zu Verhandlungen g├дbe, seien diese eher als taktische Pausen anzusehen. Das ├╝bergeordnete Ziel тАУ der Ukraine ihr Existenzrecht zu nehmen тАУ r├╝cke Russland nicht ab. Major bef├╝rwortet die Lieferung schwerer Waffen an die Ukraine: тАЮWenn Russland den Krieg gewinnt, dann wird die Sicherheitslage in Europa deutlich, deutlich schlechter aussehen als jetztтАЬ, so Major. |Auf die Frage, ob ein Atomwaffeneinsatz drohen k├╢nne, erkl├дrt Major, dies sei nicht auszuschlie├Яen, doch seien die Kosten f├╝r Russland sehr hoch. Durch sie entscheidet der Amazon-Algorithmus, welche Produkte dem Kunden zuerst angezeigt wird. Dabei sind vor allem Preis und Liefergeschwindigkeit ein wichtiges Kriterium. Oft bekommt der g├╝nstigste Anbieter mit schnellster Lieferzeit die Buy Box um sein Produkt. Der Nachteil: Alle anderen Anbieter machen kaum Verk├дufe. Denn nur ├╝ber die Buy Box kann der K├дufer seine Bestellung aufgeben. |Plusminus hat recherchiert und herausgefunden, dass H├дndler im Kampf um die Buy Box durchschnittlich mehr als 30-mal am Tag ihre Preise ├дndern. H├дndler, mit denen Plusminus sprechen konnte, bezweifeln, dass f├╝r Amazon als H├дndler die gleichen Spielregeln wie f├╝r die anderen H├дndler gelten. title: Elvis Review
description: Baz Luhrmann's Elvis is a dizzying and at times even overwhelming chronicle of the rock icon. Austin Butler is stellar as Elvis, giving it his absolute all in every scene. Tom Hanks cleverly plays against type as the manipulative and greedy Colonel Parker. While the supporting cast isn't given as many dimensions as they could have been in say, a TV miniseries, Luhrmann tells Presley's story on a grand scale suited only for the big screen, delivering an epic yet intimate maelstrom of emotions, music, ideas, and eye candy. The film's breathless pacing may befit the fevered lifestyle of a rock star, but it can also rush through necessary moments of dramatic reflection. Baz Luhrmann's Elvis is a wild ride clearly made with a big hunk o' love for its subject, and that zeal for capturing Presley's humanity, both by its director and its star, outweighs the film's excesses and shortcomings in the end. Elvis made its world premiere at the Cannes Film Festival. It opens in theaters on June 24, 2022.|#IGN #Movies

title: Russian forces focus on eastern Donbas region | DW News
description: Heavy fighting has been reported in and around the industrial city of Severodonetsk - where the regional governor says at least 12 people have been killed in shelling. Moscow says it will continue its offensive until it achieves its goals. |00:00  Russia steps up attacks on eastern Donbas |01:53 Russian firepower in Kramatorsk|04:51 Governor of Luhansk Oblast, Serhiy Haidai|05:47 Why are some people not evacuating? |Governor of Luhansk Oblast: Chances for citizens' evacuation 'are getting less and less'|"The chances [of evacuating citizens from Severodonetsk and Lysychansk] are getting less and less because the road is under fire. тАж We have been able to evacuate more than 40,000 people so far. Many left on their own. Those who remain in their houses are doing so exclusively at their own will," Serhiy Volodymyrovych Haidai, the governor of Luhansk Oblast in Ukraine, told DW.|"We are evacuating people but we do not deport people. But whenever there are people who want to leave we will evacuate them. Even if there are just ten people who want to leave we will try to take them out. They are our citizens. They are Ukrainians," the governor said. On allegations that Ukrainian authorities are abandoning the last two cities under Ukrainian control in Luhansk Oblast: "If we continue to evacuate them, if doctors are still working there, if we continue supplying them with drinking water, who can say that we have abandoned them? тАж The people who are staying there are exposing everybody to danger: themselves and the people who keep bringing them water, medicine and food."|Haidai: "We are witnessing the Russian army completely destroying Sievierodonetsk. They are shelling the whole place and they don't care whether there are civilians or whether there is a hospital or a school. They are destroying all the buildings."|The governor said the region is in need of more weapons: "Long-range artillery is what we are lacking most. We need howitzers, artillery and self-propelled systems like the French Caesar howitzers or the M777 from America. These are needed to keep the enemy at a distance and to beat them."|On whether military tactics in the regions endanger civilians, Haidai said: "We will defend ourselves. This is our land. If a city is a fortress, we will use this fortress militarily. Unfortunately the Russians don't allow civilians to leave. What shall we do? Give up? title: Partygate: WhatтАЩs in the report - and what next for Boris Johnson?

title: Transporter-5 Mission
description: On Wednesday, May 25 at 2:35 p.m. ET, Falcon 9 launched the Transporter-5, SpaceXтАЩs fifth dedicated smallsat rideshare program mission, from Space Launch Complex 40 at Cape Canaveral Space Force Station in Florida. This was the eighth launch and landing of this Falcon 9 stage booster, which previously supported launch of Crew-1, Crew-2, SXM-8, CRS-23, IXPE, one Starlink mission, and Transporter-4. Following stage separation, SpaceX landed Falcon 9тАЩs first stage on Landing Zone 1 (LZ-1) at Cape Canaveral Space Force Station.|On board this flight were 59 spacecraft, including including CubeSats, microsats, non-deploying hosted payloads, and orbital transfer vehicles.

title: Why The U.S. Mortgage Market Is Broken
description: For decades, Americans have relied on mortgages to purchase a home. But experts say that several aspects of todayтАЩs mortgage market including cost, the lack of small-dollar loans and lender bias have all greatly hindered Americans from owning their own property. Can the U.S. do anything to fix the broken system and allow mortgages to improve homeownership in America? Watch the video to find out.|EditorтАЩs note and correction (May 27, 2022): A previous version of this video misstated the percentage of nationwide home sales below $100,000 in 2019. The Urban Institute is recalculating its proprietary data after an error was discovered. A similar analysis from the National Association of Realtors shows that the 2019 figure was 8.4%.|High home prices arenтАЩt the only reason behind dwindling homeownership in the U.S. Banks and financial institutions arenтАЩt issuing enough small-dollar mortgages that help families with modest incomes to purchase a property.|тАЬIt is particularly hard for people who are buying smaller houses with smaller mortgages to find a lender and to get that mortgage,тАЭ said Mike Calhoun, president of the Center for Responsible Lending. тАЬAnd they also surprisingly are more expensive.тАЭ|And the issue has been getting worse. The value of mortgage loans between $10,000 and $70,000 and between $70,000 and $150,000 dropped by more than 53% and over 21%, respectively, from 2011 to 2021, according to research by Attom Data Solutions. Meanwhile, the value for loans exceeding $150,000 rose by a staggering 240% plus in the same period.|Another study found that denial rates for small-dollar loans were notably higher than denial rates for larger loans. And itтАЩs not because these loans are riskier. Accompanying research found that applicants for small-dollar loans had similar credit profiles to applicants for larger loans.|The real reason is profit.|тАЬOne barrier for small-dollar mortgages is that itтАЩs just not as profitable for lenders to do them,тАЭ according to Janneke Ratcliffe, vice president of the Housing Finance Policy Center at the Urban Institute. тАЬLenders get all their fees and interest based on the loan amount so theyтАЩre going to get a lot less revenue on a $70,000 mortgage than they are on a $700,000 mortgage.тАЭ|┬╗ Subscribe to CNBC: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBC|┬╗ Subscribe to CNBC TV: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBCtelevision|About CNBC: From 'Wall Street' to 'Main Street' to award winning original documentaries and Reality TV series, CNBC has you covered. title: Discover Montreal's HIDDEN Supercar Mancave! Visiting the Poirier Collection
description: Welcome to the Poirier Collection! I'm in Montreal, Canada, making my way to Toronto for the Gumball 3000, but first a stop to visit the amazing private garage and ultimate mancave of Luc Poirier. From the Ferrari Big 5 to the latest supercars, let's take a look around!|When I started work on @The Shmuseum, it was exactly this kind of venue that inspired me, and continues to give me ideas and set goals for what I'd like it to become in time. Not only the cars that are part of the collection, but the way it is set up and unique elements that make it different to any other garage.|With Ferrari standing out as the number one brand; the full line up of the Ferrari supercars are featured: LaFerrari Aperta, Enzo, F50, F40 and 288 GTO. The collection continues to also include the full line of the V8 mid-engine supercars including: 488 Pista, 458 Special, 430 Scuderia Spider 16M, 360 Challenge Stradale, F355 Fiorano, 348, 328 and 308, plus the V12s: F12tdf, 599 GTO, 575 SuperAmerica, Testarossa, and more to come.|However, we can also see a Lamborghinin Aventador Ultimae, AMG GT Black Series, Porsche 992 GT3 and 992 Turbo S Cabriolet (in Rubystone Red), and some other amazing and unusual cars from a shortened classic Mini, to a Unimog!|A huge thank you to Luc and the team at the Poirier Collection for the opportunity to visit, explore, and share the dream venue!|https://www.instagram.com/lucpoirier7|Thanks for watching, Tim|Chapters:|00:00 Intro|00:51 Walkaround of the Ferrari Lineup|06:34 Checking out the Other Cars|10:10 Washing Bay|11:09 Number Plates|11:35 Fun Area|13:08 Final Look Around |14:15 Wrap Up|#PoirierCollection #Supercars #Montreal||||Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Shmee150YT||Website: http://www.shmee150.com||Shop: http://shop.shmee150.com||Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/shmee150||Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/shmee150

title: Rafale jets collide mid-air during airshow in France; Macron govt orders probe | Watch
description: Terrifying moment of two French Rafale fighter jets mid-air collision has been caught on camera. The incident happened during the Cognac airshow- at Chateaubernard military base. Colonel Nicholas Liot, commander of the military base, said the collision that happened on Sunday was 'very rare'. The top tail of one of the two jets got severed in the collision. The aircraft managed to land safely. However, the debris of the jet fell on a house in the neighbouring village, damaging its roof. The French govt and Dassault have now ordered a probe as this is the second such accident of Rafale jets in 2022. India too, has 35 Rafale jets while one more is expected to arrive soon. Watch the mid-air horror.|#RafaleJetsCollision #MidAirScare #DassaultAviation #MacronOrdersProbe

title: Mesut Ozil Sapa Fan Indonesia Bersama Sandiaga Uno: Assalamualaikum
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Bintang sepakbola asal Jerman Mesut Ozil telah hadir di Indonesia dalam rangka produk kolaborasi merk alat olahraga Concave.||||Salah satu agendanya adalah gelar konferensi pers bersama Kementerian Pariwisata dan Ekonomi Kreatif.||||Menparekraf Sandiaga Uno hadir langsung menemani Ozil di panggung. Ozil pun sampaikan rasa semangatnya datang ke Indonesia.||||Baca Juga Momen Mesut Ozil tiba di Indonesia hingga Pamer Makan Rendang di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292401/momen-mesut-ozil-tiba-di-indonesia-hingga-pamer-makan-rendang||||"Saya ingin mengatakan, Assalamualaikum. Saya sangat bersemangat ketika tahu di Indonesia, saya punya banyak pengikut di sini," ucap Ozil.||||Ia pun mengaku bahwa ia telah bertemu beberapa dari masyarakat Indonesia dan berterima kasih atas kebaikan hatinya.||||"Saya bertemu beberapa dari kalian, dan kalian amat baik. Terima kasih."||||Ozil juga diagendakan hadir ke pabrik Concave di Indonesia, tepatnya di Cikupa, Banten.||||Mesut Ozil tiba di Indonesia sejak Selasa (24/5) malam, dan disambut sejumlah penggemarnya.||||Ozil merupakan pesepakbola asal Jerman yang kini membela klub Fenerbahce.||||Nama Ozil bersinar ketika ia sempat membela dua klub besar Eropa, Real Madrid dan Arsenal.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292563/mesut-ozil-sapa-fan-indonesia-bersama-sandiaga-uno-assalamualaikum

title: Unrest in Pak as Imran Khan's Islamabad March turns violent; PTI workers clash with cops in Lahore
description: Pakistan's ousted Prime Minister Imran Khan led a convoy of thousands of supporters towards the capital Islamabad in a show of force against the new government. Clashes between Imran supporters and police broke out in Lahore and Islamabad. In a centrepiece showdown with his rivals, Khan had called for supporters to march towards the capital and stage a sit-in until fresh elections are called. Police deployed tear gas against hundreds of Khan backers attempting to remove roadblocks in Lahore and Faizabad, where PTI supporters also seized an excavator to clear the route of containers. Watch this video for more.|#Pakistan #Lahore #AzadiMarch #ImranKhan #ShehbazSharif #Pak #Islamabad #Elections #PTI #PPP #Imran #Protest

title: Sniper Elite 5 Review
description: Reviewed by Tristan Ogilvie on Xbox Series X. Also available on Xbox, PlayStation, and PC.||||"Despite its numerous tweaks Sniper Elite 5 ultimately feels like more of an incremental upgrade than a major revolution, keeping it a half-pace ahead of Sniper Elite 4 rather than taking a big goose-step forward for the series. With a more manoeuvrable main star, modifiable weapons, enhanced co-op, and Axis Invasion allowing the hunter to become the hunted, Sniper Elite 5 is still a satisfying and spectacularly gross way to shoot Nazis in their nether regions -- but it feels like the series needs to start aiming its sights a little higher and find ways to avoid repeating the same handful of objectives so often."

title: Manoj Sinha Meets Cricketer Umran Malik In Jammu, Promises Support
description: Jammu and Kashmir Lieutenant Governor Manoj Sinha on Tuesday evening met pace sensation Umran Malik here and said the administration will take care of his training and other facilities. Malik, who received his maiden call-up for the national team for the upcoming five-match T20 International home series against South Africa starting June 9, reached his Jammu residence on Monday after taking part in the Indian Premier League (IPL). The whole country is proud (of Umran). The government will take care of his training and other facilities," Sinha told reporters after meeting Malik. title: UK evacuation from Afghanistan judged 'a disaster' - BBC Newsnight

title: Ozil Jawab Kemungkinan Main di Indonesia, Sebut Akan Pilih Bali United
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Bintang sepakbola asal Jerman Mesut Ozil menyebut tak menutup kemungkinan untuk bermain di Indonesia.||||Hal tersebut ia ungkapkan saat menjawab pertanyaan wartawan soal kemungkinan berkarier di Indonesia.||||Ia mengatakan kini dirinya terikat kontrak dengan klub Turki, Fenerbahce. Namun ia akan memilih sebuah klub jika diberi kesempatan main di Indonesia.||||Baca Juga Mesut Ozil Sapa Fan Indonesia Bersama Sandiaga Uno: Assalamualaikum di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292563/mesut-ozil-sapa-fan-indonesia-bersama-sandiaga-uno-assalamualaikum||||"Saya masih dalam kontrak di Turki, bersama Fenerbahce. Saya senang berada di sana," ucap Ozil.||||"Jika saya berkesempatan untuk bermain di Indonesia, saya memilih Bali United," lanjutnya.||||Bintang sepakbola asal Jerman Mesut Ozil telah hadir di Indonesia dalam rangka produk kolaborasi merk alat olahraga Concave.||||Salah satu agendanya adalah gelar konferensi pers bersama Kementerian Pariwisata dan Ekonomi Kreatif.||||Menparekraf Sandiaga Uno hadir langsung menemani Ozil di panggung. Ozil pun sampaikan rasa semangatnya datang ke Indonesia.||||"Saya ingin mengatakan, Assalamualaikum. Saya sangat bersemangat ketika tahu di Indonesia, saya punya banyak pengikut di sini," ucap Ozil.||||Ia pun mengaku bahwa ia telah bertemu beberapa dari masyarakat Indonesia dan berterima kasih atas kebaikan hatinya.||||"Saya bertemu beberapa dari kalian, dan kalian amat baik. Terima kasih."||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292594/ozil-jawab-kemungkinan-main-di-indonesia-sebut-akan-pilih-bali-united
